WSL SETUP
---------
sudo apt update
sudo apt install make -y
make --version


PROJECT STRUCTURE
-----------------
calculator/
├── calculator.go
├── Makefile
├── logs/
├── go.mod


MAKEFILE
--------
APP=calculator

run:
	go run calculator.go

build:
	go build -o $(APP)

clean:
	rm -f $(APP)
	rm -rf logs

fmt:
	go fmt ./...

test:
	go test ./...


HOW TO RUN (WSL ONLY)
--------------------
make run

make build
./calculator 10 + 5

make fmt
make test
make clean
